The House of Representatives on Tuesday asked President Muhammadu Buhari to immediately declare a state of emergency on the security situation in the country. The House resolution was part of the decision taken after a three- hour executive session, which also demanded immediate recruitment of personnel into the Police and military. It lamented personnel in the services fall short of requirements. The House also summoned the National Security Adviser, service chiefs and the Director General of NIGCOMSAT for briefing on security situation in the country. Details shortlyâ€¦